<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span>ترتيبها ٦٦ ... سُورَةُ التَّحْرِيمِ ... آياتها ١٢ مدنية<a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p2"></span>الآية ... الكلمة ... معناها<a href="#p2" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p3"></span><span class="c2">(٢)</span> ... <span class="c3">{تَحِلَّةَ أَيْمَانِكُمْ}</span> ... تَحْلِيلَ أَيْمَانِكُمْ بِأَدَاءِ الكَفَّارَةِ عَنْهَا.<a href="#p3" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p4"></span><span class="c2">(٢)</span> ... <span class="c3">{مَوْلَاكُمْ}</span> ... نَاصِرُكُمْ، وَمُتَوَلِّي أُمُورِكُمْ.<a href="#p4" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p5"></span><span class="c2">(٣)</span> ... <span class="c3">{بَعْضِ أَزْوَاجِهِ}</span> ...<span class="c5"> هِيَ:</span> حَفْصَةُ بِنْتُ عُمَرَ رضي الله عنهما.<a href="#p5" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p6"></span><span class="c2">(٣)</span> ... <span class="c3">{وَأَظْهَرَهُ}</span> ... أَطْلَعَهُ.<a href="#p6" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p7"></span><span class="c2">(٣)</span> ... <span class="c3">{عَرَّفَ بَعْضَهُ}</span> ... أَعْلَمَ حَفْصَةَ رَضِيَ اللهُ عَنْهَا بَعْضَ مَا أَخْبَرَتْ بِهِ.<a href="#p7" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p8"></span><span class="c2">(٤)</span> ... <span class="c3">{تَتُوبَا إِلَى اللَّهِ}</span> ... تَرْجِعَا - يَا حَفْصَةُ، وَيَا عَائِشَةُ - إِلَى اللهِ.<a href="#p8" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p9"></span><span class="c2">(٤)</span> ... <span class="c3">{صَغَتْ قُلُوبُكُمَا}</span> ... مَالَتْ إِلَى مَحَبَّةِ مَا كَرِهَهُ الرَّسُولُ - صلى الله عليه وسلم - مِنْ إِفْشَاءِ سِرِّهِ.<a href="#p9" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p10"></span><span class="c2">(٤)</span> ... <span class="c3">{وَإِن تَظَاهَرَا عَلَيْهِ}</span> ... وَإِنْ تَتَعَاوَنَا عَلَيْهِ.<a href="#p10" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p11"></span><span class="c2">(٤)</span> ... <span class="c3">{ظَهِيرٌ}</span> ... أَعْوَانٌ، وَأَنْصَارٌ.<a href="#p11" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p12"></span><span class="c2">(٥)</span> ... <span class="c3">{سَائِحَاتٍ}</span> ... صَائِمَاتٍ.<a href="#p12" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p13"></span><span class="c2">(٨)</span> ... <span class="c3">{تَوْبَةً نَّصُوحًا}</span> ... صَادِقَةً لَا يَعُودُ صَاحِبُهَا إِلَى الذَّنْبِ، وَلَا يُرِيدُ العَوْدَ إِلَيْهِ.<a href="#p13" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p14"></span><span class="c2">(٨)</span> ... <span class="c3">{لَا يُخْزِي}</span> ... لَا يُذِلُّ، وَلَا يُعَذِّبُ.<a href="#p14" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p15"></span><span class="c2">(٨)</span> ... <span class="c3">{يَسْعَى}</span> ... يَسِيرُ.<a href="#p15" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p16"></span><span class="c2">(٨)</span> ... <span class="c3">{بَيْنَ أَيْدِيهِمْ}</span> ... أَمَامَهُمْ.<a href="#p16" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>